  title: "Why use a separate script for the StatsUI? Can\u2019t I just do it in the
    GameManager?"
  text: "You *could*, but separating your UI from your game logic makes the code
    cleaner and more modular. The UI just reads values from the logic scripts\u2014it
    doesn\u2019t control anything. That separation makes it easier to maintain and
    avoids messy dependencies."
